    "answer": "(1) $\\\\mathbf{P}_i + \\mathbf{P}_e = \\mathbf{P}_f + \\mathbf{P}_{e}'$。\\n(2) $E_f = \\\\frac{E_i}{1 + \\\\frac{E_i}{m_e c^2}(1 - \\\\cos \\\\theta)}$；证明过程见下。",
    "reasoning_process": "(1) 设光子入射四维动量为 $\\mathbf{P}_i$，静止电子为 $\\mathbf{P}_e$，散射后光子为 $\\mathbf{P}_f$，反冲电子为 $\\mathbf{P}_{e}'$。根据守恒律：\n$$\\mathbf{P}_i + \\mathbf{P}_e = \\mathbf{P}_f + \\mathbf{P}_{e}'$$\n\n(2) 证明：\n移项得 $\\mathbf{P}_e + \\mathbf{P}_i - \\mathbf{P}_f = \\mathbf{P}_{e}'$。\n两边取模平方（利用 Minkowski 度规）：\n$(\\mathbf{P}_e + \\mathbf{P}_i - \\mathbf{P}_f)^2 = (\\mathbf{P}_{e}')^2$\n$\\mathbf{P}_e^2 + \\mathbf{P}_i^2 + \\mathbf{P}_f^2 + 2\\mathbf{P}_e \\cdot \\mathbf{P}_i - 2\\mathbf{P}_e \\cdot \\mathbf{P}_f - 2\\mathbf{P}_i \\cdot \\mathbf{P}_f = m_e^2 c^2$\n已知：$\\mathbf{P}_e^2 = m_e^2 c^2$, $\\mathbf{P}_i^2 = 0$, $\\mathbf{P}_f^2 = 0$。\n$\\mathbf{P}_e = (m_e c, 0, 0, 0)$，故 $\\mathbf{P}_e \\cdot \\mathbf{P}_i = m_e E_i$，$\\mathbf{P}_e \\cdot \\mathbf{P}_f = m_e E_f$。\n$\\mathbf{P}_i \\cdot \\mathbf{P}_f = \\frac{E_i E_f}{c^2} - \\vec{p}_i \\cdot \\vec{p}_f = \\frac{E_i E_f}{c^2}(1 - \\cos \\theta)$。\n代入上式：\n$m_e^2 c^2 + 0 + 0 + 2m_e E_i - 2m_e E_f - 2\\frac{E_i E_f}{c^2}(1 - \\cos \\theta) = m_e^2 c^2$\n$m_e(E_i - E_f) = \\frac{E_i E_f}{c^2}(1 - \\cos \\theta)$\n整理得：$\\frac{1}{E_f} - \\frac{1}{E_i} = \\frac{1}{m_e c^2}(1 - \\cos \\theta)$\n即 $E_f = \\frac{E_i}{1 + \\frac{E_i}{m_e c^2}(1 - \\cos \\theta)}$。\n\n由于 $\\lambda = \\frac{hc}{E}$，则 $\\frac{\\lambda_f}{hc} - \\frac{\\lambda_i}{hc} = \\frac{1}{m_e c^2}(1 - \\cos \\theta)$。\n$\\Delta \\lambda = \\lambda_f - \\lambda_i = \\frac{h}{m_e c}(1 - \\cos \\theta)$。得证。"
